---
title: Longhorn Turkey & Black Bean Chili with Jalapeño & Smoky Red Pepper Crema
description: A good chili has well-seasoned meat, creamy beans, and tender veggies. A great chili, however, has all that and comes together in one pot in under an hour. This chili is one of the greats. And once you take a bite, we can guarantee you’ll agree. Not to mention, these top-notch turkey-fied bowls are adorned with some delicious fixings: smoky red pepper crema and sliced jalepeño. If you’ve got some on hand, why not crumble up some tortilla chips and sprinkle them on top for a crunch?
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/turkey-black-bean-chili-6911ec2f.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/longhorn-turkey-black-bean-chili-602c3dc9959864365c653930-9fe68579.pdf
